  <h1>Retail Jobs: Start Your Career Quickly</h1>

  <p>Retail jobs are one of the fastest ways to enter the workforce. These roles involve working in stores, helping customers, and managing sales operations.</p>

  <h2>Common Retail Roles</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Store Assistant</li>
    <li>Cashier</li>
    <li>Sales Associate</li>
    <li>Store Manager</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Skills Required</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Customer service skills</li>
    <li>Communication</li>
    <li>Teamwork</li>
    <li>Basic math skills</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Why Choose Retail?</h2>
  <p>Retail jobs offer flexible hours, quick hiring, and opportunities to grow into management roles.</p>

  <h2>Where to Find Jobs</h2>
  <p>Shopping malls, supermarkets, and brand outlets frequently hire retail staff.</p>

